The '''Keren Grand Arch''' was an arch that stood at the end of one of the canals that ran through the city of [[Keren/Legends|Keren]] on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]].

{{Struct-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The arch is similar in appearance to the [[Triumphal Arch/Legends|Triumphal Arch]] in the capital [[Theed/Legends|Theed]].

